    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled right off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it\u2019s been kept sparkling clean and garage-stored. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on it. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat more about it!",
