    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the revered S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that operates with surgical precision. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. This specimen features a reinforced rear subframe and a pristine chassis free of any fatigue or oxidation. Every bushing, link, and damper remains within factory tolerances, providing the communicative steering rack feedback and lateral stability these icons are known for. A mechanically flawless, turnkey example for the purist who demands an uncompromised driving experience.",
